<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>URL Shortener</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>URL Shortner</h1>
    <div class="list">
      <h2>User Stories</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.</li>
        <li>When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="code-group">
        <h2>Sample Input</h2>
        <code>localhost:3000/create/www.google.com</code>
        <br>
        <code>localhost:3000/create/notAValidURL</code>
      </div>
      <div class="code-group">
        <h2>Sample Output</h2>
        <code>{ "success": true, "original_url": "www.google.com", "short_url": "localhost:3000/goto/ryjYGfll-"}</code>
        <br>
        <code>{ "success": false, "msg": "Invalid URL" }</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
